body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, this is Vincent Perry from Secure Auto Solutions. May I know your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Joyce. Can you provide me with your date of birth?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's January twenty five, ninteen seventy five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. And could you also share your home address with us?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, it's one two three Main Street, Cityville, State ABC, one two three four five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great! We have noted down your information, Joyce. Is there anything else you'd like to share with us today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all for now. I'm just excited about the new security features at the dealership.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: We're thrilled to hear that you're excited, Joyce. Thank you for your time and for choosing Secure Auto Solutions. Have a wonderful day!
